  %% Diagram 56: Unified Notification Center Orchestration Flow

  Event[Incoming domain event]
  Classify[Classify event type and severity]
  Prefs[Evaluate user channel preferences]
  Matrix[Build primary and fallback channel matrix]

  Channels[Available channels\nIn-app, WhatsApp, Push/Web]
  PrimarySend[Send via selected primary channel]

  Delivered[(Update notification center state delivered)]
  Read[(Update notification center state read)]
  Fail{Primary channel delivered?}
  Reroute[Reroute to allowed fallback channels]
  FallbackSend[Send through fallback channels]

  Event --> Classify --> Prefs --> Matrix --> Channels --> PrimarySend

  PrimarySend --> Fail

  Fail -- Yes --> Delivered --> Read
  Fail -- No --> Reroute --> FallbackSend --> Delivered --> Read
